          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1685546179550-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1685546184226-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1685546184226-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1685546184226-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1685546184226-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1685546184226-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> chopped coriander</strong>, <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lime</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> and mix well – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges for garnish</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1685546188117-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
